assies ==\n*{{CAN}}\n*{{EST}}\n*{{LIT}}\n*{{MEX}}\n*{{SUD}}\n*{{SWE}}\n\n== See also ==\n* [[Foreign relations of Bulgaria]]\n* [[Visa requirements for Bulgarian citizens]]\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n=== External links ===\n* [http://www.mfa.bg/setlang/en/ Bulgarian Ministry of Foreign Affairs]\n\n{{Foreign relations of Bulgaria}}\n\n{{Europe topic|List of diplomatic missions in|countries_only=yes}}\n\n[[Category:Foreign relations of Bulgaria]]\n[[Category:Lists of diplomatic missions by receiving country|Bulgaria]]\n[[Category:Bulgaria diplomacy-related lists|Diplomatic missions]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Wikipedia list article}}\n[[File:Diplomatic missions in Bulgaria.PNG|thumb|right|400px|Map of diplomatic missions in Bulgaria]]\nThis page lists diplomatic missions resident in [[Bulgaria]]. At present, the capital city of [[Sofia]] hosts 71 embassies.\n\nThis listing excludes honorary consulates.\n\n== Embassies ==\n[[File:Albanian-Embassy-in-Sofia.JPG|thumb|right|Embassy of Albania in Sofia]]\n[[File:Armenian-embassy-in-Sofia.jpg|thumb|right|Embassy of Armenia in Sofia]]\n[[File:Sofia TodorBozhinov 30 September (4).JPG|thumb|right|Embassy of Egypt in Sofia]]\n[[File:Sofia buildings TodorBozhinov (26).JPG|thumb|right|Embassy of France in Sofia]]\n[[File:Greek embassy in Sofia 2012 PD IMG 2746.jpg|thumb|right|Embassy of Greece in Sofia]]\n[[File:Sofia buildings TodorBozhinov (25).JPG|thumb|right|Embassy of the Netherlands in Sofia]]\n[[File:Ambasada RP w Sofii od p\u00f3\u0142nocy1.jpg|thumb|right|Embassy of Poland in Sofia]]\n[[File:\u041f\u043e\u0441\u043e\u043b\u0441\u0442\u0432\u043e \u043d\u0430 \u041f\u043e\u0440\u0442\u0443\u0433\u0430\u043b\u0438\u044f \u0432 \u0421\u043e\u0444\u0438\u044f, \u0411\u044a\u043b\u0433\u0430\u0440\u0438\u044f.JPG|thumb|right|Embassy of Portugal in Sofia]]\n[[File:Ambasada-romaniei.jpg|thumb|right|Embassy of Romania in Sofia]]\n[[File:Russian Embassy - Sofia.jpg|thumb|right|Embassy of Russia in Sofia]]\n[[F